Package: oar-api
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, oar-common (>= 2.4.0), oar-user (>= 2.4.0), ${perl:Depends}, httpd-cgi, perl-modules, libjson-perl, libwww-perl, libcgi-fast-perl
Suggests: oar-doc
